- Add _BP_SYNONYMS map (extensible, variant phrasings → canonical key)
- Add _bpNormalizeQuery() — apostrophe normalization + synonym resolution
- Update _bpTranslate() — apostrophe-normalized fallback lookup
- _bpRunSearch uses normQ for translation (not raw query)
- Layer 5 fallback: if score filter empties results but raw had candidates,
