MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Critical fix: fuzzy matching was in _bpScore (post-OFX) but typos in the QUERY
(e.g. "ניר טואלט", "קוטץ") prevent OFX from returning candidates at all.
Fixed by adding fuzzy token lookup inside _bpTranslate so bad spellings still
produce an English search term before hitting the API.

Algorithm: requires ALL query tokens to fuzzy-match (dist≤1) within the SAME
dict key — prevents "ניר מגבת" from falsely mapping to "toilet paper" via the
shared "ניר"≈"נייר" token hit alone. Verified with Node.js test suite.

Synonyms added: קוטץ→קוטג' (ץ/ג typo), ניר טואלט→נייר טואלט (missing yod),
ניר מגבת→נייר מגבת, ניר טואלת→נייר טואלט

Dict entries added: נוזל כלים, נייר אפייה, ספריי ניקוי

Minor: fallback notice "מציגים תוצאות דומות" (spec wording),
log field finalCount→resultCount

